      <title>顶级石油交易商表示 OPEC+ 几乎没有增加供应的空间</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-26/top-oil-traders-say-opec-has-little-room-to-increase-supply</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一些全球顶级能源贸易机构表示，在恢复一直未向市场供应的石油产能方面，OPEC+ 几乎没有选择。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-26/top-oil-traders-say-opec-has-little-room-to-increase-supply</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 26 Nov 2024 18:01:34 GMT</pubDate>
