    <item>
      <title>埃克森美孚称特朗普执政期间不太可能推行“钻探，宝贝，钻探”政策</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-26/-drill-baby-drill-is-unlikely-under-trump-exxon-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[埃克森美孚上游业务总裁利亚姆马龙表示，尽管当选总统唐纳德特朗普呼吁“钻探，宝贝，钻探”，但美国的石油和天然气生产商在未来几年不会大幅提高产量。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-26/-drill-baby-drill-is-unlikely-under-trump-exxon-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 26 Nov 2024 10:37:16 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
